{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b6ab8da5b0","title":"大字报诗—— “琵琶行”","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（一）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2c7c0dd226","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1471f995a2","name":"张文华"},{"id":"79af059482","name":"山西师范学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1ea17db768","type":"title","text":"大字报诗—— “琵琶行”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"3d16c533ff","type":"authors","text":"山西师范学院张文华","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"34625360df","type":"subtitle","text":"“琵琶行”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"08001ac4a1","type":"paragraph","text":"活剖孕妇商纣王，焚书坑儒秦始皇，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"f808e4870b","type":"paragraph","text":"二十世纪中青王，怀抱琵琶苏院长。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"773995294e","type":"paragraph","text":" 山西师范学院  张文华","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"fd8cec3ba1","type":"subtitle","text":"写在厕所的诗","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"c000403e2b","type":"paragraph","text":"争鸣狂风过，百花气节伤。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"491c68b883","type":"paragraph","text":"恨迹大路旁，目睹心悽凉。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"878edf0d93","type":"paragraph","text":"秋冬之际春风来，百花含苞欲放开。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"10d202202d","type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜暴风铺满地，此情此景实可哀。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"d396c2ca58","type":"paragraph","text":"说争鸣，道争鸣，争鸣成了一阵风。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"acf1db207c","type":"paragraph","text":"只怕风过天又雨，大家徒劳一场空。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"81b155d6c9","type":"paragraph","text":" 山西师范学院×××","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"43900b924e","type":"subtitle","text":"致在墙角写诗的人们","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"8a7a155070","type":"paragraph","text":"说争鸣，道争鸣，争鸣来了一阵风，只说风吹乌云散，那知风吹云更浓，用风不行用药，用药不行用刀，用刀不行用火，火！火！烧掉那些恶东西。在墙角写诗的朋友，把诗印在火把上，挺身出来，你的朋友在等待着你。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"8983255c19","type":"paragraph","text":" 山西师院  马后炮","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"82250563b5","type":"subtitle","text":"“西江月”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"4bb88813e0","type":"paragraph","text":"乌云遮住了太阳，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"b4531dd678","type":"paragraph","text":"百姓要见阳光，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"2bef6a83b3","type":"paragraph","text":"手拿风煽，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"db4390fb7a","type":"paragraph","text":"赶散乌云，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"24b29f27eb","type":"paragraph","text":"为了大放大鸣。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"},{"id":"de3c3027f6","type":"paragraph","text":" 山西师范学院×××","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0"}],"page":{"id":"fd8fe84edc","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b6ab8da5b0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}